1392527 c (i) the constitution of the Executive Committee or other committees and the functions thereof;
558999 iithe time and place at which such committees shall meet; and
323767 iiithe rules of procedure (including quorum) which shall be observed by each Committee in relation to the transaction of business at its meetings, as required by section 15;
490814 dfees and allowances which may be paid to the directors and members of the committee, as required by section 17;
